generatorType.name: Fader
generatorType.description: Fades linear from a start to a end value.

inputType.name: startFadeValue
inputType.description: Start value between -1 and 1 of the fading over generator length (other value ranges can used).

inputType.name: endFadeValue
inputType.description: End value between -1 and 1 of the fading over generator length (other value ranges can used).

generatorType.name: Mixer
generatorType.description: Mixes multiple signal input lines and scale them with a volume.

inputType.name: volume
inputType.description: The volume of the output singal between 0 and 1 (average is calculated if more then one volume is connected).

inputType.name: signal
inputType.description: The input signal between -1 and 1 (average is calculated if more then one volume is connected).

generatorType.name: Multiplier
generatorType.description: Multiply multiple signal input lines and multiply them with a multiplier.

inputType.name: multiplier
inputType.description: The volume of the output singal between 0 and 1 (average is calculated if more then one volume is connected).

inputType.name: signal
inputType.description: The input signal between -1 and 1 (average is calculated if more then one volume is connected).

generatorType.name: Sinus
generatorType.description: Generates a sinus signal with a specified frequency and amplidude.

inputType.name: signalFrequency
inputType.description: Frequency of the signal in oscillations per second (alternativ to signalInput).

inputType.name: signalAmplitude
inputType.description: Amplidude of the signal between 0 and 1.

inputType.name: signalShift
inputType.description: The offset of the sinus between -1 and 1 (0 is no shift, 0.5 is shifting a half oscillation).

inputType.name: signalInput
inputType.description: Input of the sinus signal (alternativ to signalFrequency).

generatorType.name: Rectangle
generatorType.description: Generates a rectangle signal with a specified frequency and amplidude.

inputType.name: signalFrequency
inputType.description: Frequency of the signal in oscillations per second.

inputType.name: signalAmplitude
inputType.description: Amplidude of the signal between 0 and 1.

inputType.name: signalShift
inputType.description: The offset of the rectangle between -1 and 1 (0 is no shift, 0.5 is shifting a half oscillation).

generatorType.name: Cut

inputType.name: signalFrequency
inputType.description: Frequency of the pulse in oscillations per second.

inputType.name: signalAmplitude
inputType.description: Amplidude of the pulse between 0 and 1.

inputType.name: attackTime
inputType.description: The attack time of the pulse in percent between 0.0 and 1.0.

inputType.name: sustainTime
inputType.description: The sustain time of the pulse in percent between 0.0 and 1.0.

inputType.name: releaseTime
inputType.description: The release time of the pulse in percent between 0.0 and 1.0.
